  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bc6\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bc1 : \u0b9c\u0bc2\u0bb2\u0bc8\u200b 10 \u0b86\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb9\u0b9c\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bca\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0b9f \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Headline appeared: Resolution to celebrate Hajj on July 10th",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the headline of the month of Tul Hajj appearing in some parts of the country today, it has been decided to celebrate the upcoming Eid-ul-Azha Hajj on the 10th.",
        "The conference to decide the theme of the month of Tul Hajj was held today at the Colombo Grand Mosque after the Mahrif prayers.",
        "Meanwhile, the Colombo Grand Mosque announced that it had found evidence of headline-grabbing in some parts of the country.",
        "Accordingly, it has been decided to celebrate the upcoming Eid-ul-Azha Hajj in Sri Lanka on Sunday the 10th."
      ],
